Senior Corporate Associate, Abu Dhabi, 6+PQE
Senior Corporate Associate, Abu Dhabi, 6+PQE
Location:  --Abu Dhabi
This highly regarded and well established law firm is urgently seeking a senior Corporate Commercial Associate who has very strong M&E transactional experience, to be based in Abu Dhabi. The ideal candidate will be 6+ PQE and can be either bilingual or Western. You should have solid private practice experience at reputable firms; UAE and regional experience would be an advantage.
The teams experience includes share and business acquisitions and disposals, corporate structuring and licensing, joint ventures and private equity, as well as general corporate, commercial and regulatory matters. Clients include local and international private sector and governmental organisations.
